query:
ALTER TABLE users 
ADD COLUMN phoneNumber varchar(32),
ADD COLUMN userRole enum('public','marked_initiate','marked_member','marked_inner_circle','staff','admin') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'public',
ADD COLUMN userStatus enum('active','revoked','banned') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active',
ADD COLUMN callSign varchar(64),
ADD COLUMN chapter varchar(128) DEFAULT 'South Jakarta',
ADD COLUMN markState enum('outside','initiate','member','inner_circle','dormant','restricted','revoked') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'outside',
ADD COLUMN rankDate timestamp NULL,
ADD COLUMN clearanceState enum('none','applied','granted','expired','denied') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'none',
ADD COLUMN clearanceExpiresAt timestamp NULL,
ADD COLUMN clearanceCode varchar(32),
ADD COLUMN invitesAvailable int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN reputationPoints int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN referralCode varchar(32),
ADD COLUMN lastActiveAt timestamp NULL,
ADD COLUMN revokedReason text,
ADD COLUMN revokedAt timestamp NULL,
ADD COLUMN revokedById int;
